flowchart TD
    A([Start: drift analyze old_file new_file]) --> B[Initialize components<br/>CSVLoader, SchemaAnalyzer, TypeChecker,<br/>RowComparator, ExplainabilityEngine]

    B --> C[Build ReportConfig<br/>format, output, summary_only,<br/>verbose, no_color, strict]
    C --> D[Create ReportGenerator config]

    D --> E[Load files]
    E --> E1[Load old file]
    E1 --> E2[Load new file]

    E2 --> F[Analyze schema differences]
    F --> G[Find common columns]
    G --> H[Compare types]

    H --> K[Detect key column]
    K --> M{Key column exists?}

    M -- No --> N[Set row_diff empty]
    M -- Yes --> O{Key in both datasets?}

    O -- No --> P[Print key error]
    P --> X1([Exit 1])

    O -- Yes --> Q[Compare rows]
    Q --> R[Convert result to dict]
    N --> S
    R --> S

    S[Calculate severity]
    S --> T[Generate explanations]
    T --> U[Get change summary]
    U --> V[Explain impact]

    V --> W[Assemble results]
    W --> Y[Generate report]

    Y --> Z{Output path provided?}
    Z -- Yes --> Z1[Save report + print path]
    Z -- No --> AA[Skip save]

    Z1 --> AB[Emit report]
    AA --> AB
    AB --> AC([Exit 0])

    E -->|FileNotFoundError| X2[Print error]
    F -->|ValueError| X3[Print error]
    G -->|Exception| X4[Unexpected error]
    H -->|Exception| X4
    Y -->|Exception| X4

    X2 --> X5([Exit 1])
    X3 --> X5
    X4 --> X5
